<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
 <User xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
 xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal">
 <OxID tal:condition="python: options.has_key('person_id')" tal:content="options/person_id">0</OxID>
 <Email tal:condition="python: options.has_key('email')" tal:content="options/email">useremail@domain.com</Email>
 <FirstName tal:condition="python: options.has_key('firstname')" tal:content="options/firstname">Enter User First Name</FirstName>
 <LastName tal:condition="python: options.has_key('lastname')" tal:content="options/lastname">Enter User Last Name</LastName>
 <Company tal:condition="python: options.has_key('relation')" tal:content="options/relation">Oxatis</Company>
 <BillingAddress tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_street')" tal:content="options/billing_address_street">Billing address</BillingAddress>
 <BillingAddressL1 tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_street_l1')" tal:content="options/billing_address_street_l1">Billing address</BillingAddressL1>
 <BillingAddressL2 tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_street_l2')" tal:content="options/billing_address_street_l2">Billing address</BillingAddressL2>
 <BillingAddressL3 tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_street_l3')" tal:content="options/billing_address_street_l3">Billing address</BillingAddressL3>
 <BillingAddressL4 tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_street_l4')" tal:content="options/billing_address_street_l4">Billing address</BillingAddressL4>
 <BillingZipCode tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_zip')" tal:content="options/billing_address_zip">13015</BillingZipCode>
 <BillingCity tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_city')" tal:content="options/billing_address_city">Billing city</BillingCity>
 <BillingCountryISOCode tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_address_country')" tal:content="options/billing_address_country"></BillingCountryISOCode>
 <BillingPhone tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_phone')" tal:content="options/billing_phone">Billing phone</BillingPhone>
 <BillingCellPhone tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_cellphone')"
 tal:content="options/billing_cellphone">Billing cell phone</BillingCellPhone>
 <BillingFax tal:condition="python: options.has_key('billing_fax')" tal:content="options/billing_fax"> </BillingFax>
 <CustomerAccount tal:condition="python: options.has_key('is_customer')" tal:content="options/is_customer">false</CustomerAccount>
 </User>
